Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}本当に現実なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:20.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}心がまだ追いついて来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:23.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}今は想像出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:28.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}この先押し寄せる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:32.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}Still,I have to keep going this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:34.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}あなたが居ない世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}miss you so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:39.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}消えないこの鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}会いたいあの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:49.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}もう一度近づきたい話したい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:52.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}I know life can be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:59.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}最後の言葉をねぇちゃんと聞かせてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:03.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}I wish you would stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}紫苑の花束を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:11.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}I can not live without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:15.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}あなたに捧げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}It's time to say goodbye. Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:30.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}It's time to say goodbye. Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:34.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}It's sad to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.64,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}这真的是现实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:20.31,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我的心还来不及认清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:23.98,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}眼下还无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:28.24,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}这奔涌而来的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:32.03,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我依旧要在这世间前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:34.54,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}在这没有了你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.25,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我是如此想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:39.96,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}这永不消弭的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.88,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}多想再见到你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:49.18,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}想再一次贴近你 与你欢谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:52.10,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}我已知晓 生命竟能如此煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:59.35,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}你最后的话语 我多么想要听到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:03.40,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}只愿你能与我相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.40,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}将这紫苑花束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:11.28,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}我的生命不能没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:15.95,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}奉献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.29,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}是时候与你说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:30.01,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}是时候与你说再见了
